{"tid":988681,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"★ [g嬸舊歌台] 本週精選 ：柏安妮 🙄","createTime":"2019-01-20T09:31:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-22T03:12:17.000Z","uid":44730,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"27b818f34dddc6854a17ab30ea3ed3a33ecf9c8c","tid":988681,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T09:31:39.000Z","msg":"柏安妮（Ann Bridgewater），中、英、馬來西亞混血兒，父親是一位英國醫生，家境尚算富裕，她曾獲牛津大學錄取，不過當時為加入娛樂圈便放棄學業。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://funstory.org/images/image/0/10628.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffunstory.org%2Fimages%2Fimage%2F0%2F10628.jpg&h=1a2aeab0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-LAXBGw4IyQ0/VM9heO0nhwI/AAAAAAABCAM/Dbehn24_110/s640/cu5010.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-LAXBGw4IyQ0%2FVM9heO0nhwI%2FAAAAAAABCAM%2FDbehn24_110%2Fs640%2Fcu5010.jpg&h=39bec650&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://images.miiqu.com/uploads/star/p/p_b/p_15118713635.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.miiqu.com%2Fuploads%2Fstar%2Fp%2Fp_b%2Fp_15118713635.jpg&h=26f3f129&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-atl3-1.cdninstagram.com/vp/01765fccf368505542b5e752e83db7d6/5C5FEB2E/t51.2885-15/e35/39124043_463081100856445_7247433054854053888_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-atl3-1.cdninstagram.com%2Fvp%2F01765fccf368505542b5e752e83db7d6%2F5C5FEB2E%2Ft51.2885-15%2Fe35%2F39124043_463081100856445_7247433054854053888_n.jpg&h=defa5bbb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://d.ifengimg.com/mw640_q100/p3.ifengimg.com/yidian/2017_17/18b5d4c675ce89e_w500_h272.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fd.ifengimg.com%2Fmw640_q100%2Fp3.ifengimg.com%2Fyidian%2F2017_17%2F18b5d4c675ce89e_w500_h272.jpg&h=9d9b72ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i2.wp.com/5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20180527/1dd77f0a9a004923a9df941dc9f112b7.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi2.wp.com%2F5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com%2Fimages%2F20180527%2F1dd77f0a9a004923a9df941dc9f112b7.jpeg&h=bb7a1adf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"676d7232fda212f921d829aa3aa3723b9397d6fb","tid":988681,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T09:31:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/X8yzvoKeLyk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FX8yzvoKeLyk&d=HiUNBysZrE9nbvaLZxqmO%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=55b39066\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/X8yzvoKeLyk</a><br />\n<br />\n《尖東》 <br />\n<br />\n首張大碟主打，代表年輕人玩樂之地，那裡有disco、購物商場、海旁，原曲是64年的優雅舞曲「Downtown」，促使柏安妮改編的，是88年歐洲DJ推出的Euro Disco Dance。《尖東》的佻皮歌詞唱到《天宮》，和大唱《天庭》的《神仙也移民》是兄妹作。柏安妮85年演出電影《為妳鍾情》，飾演張國榮的妹，接著出現於開心少女系列2《開心樂園》，成為少女組之一但沒有錄碟，88年加盟樂壇時，和張國榮一齊簽陳淑芬做經理人，因此經常與張國榮有不少合作，包括拍《熱辣辣》MV和一起演出88年東京音樂節，可惜因為張國榮離開華星時得罪無線高層，陳淑芬安排柏安妮入亞視，在細台宣傳一定輸蝕，兩張唱片未能大hit，只能成為小眾心頭好。"},{"pid":"a7b26f7d975d4d13f83d758949fc7c859ae39872","tid":988681,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T09:32:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://07.imgmini.eastday.com/mobile/20180609/20180609191352_a36e59cff88b5c7578ea595c1c017d21_2.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F07.imgmini.eastday.com%2Fmobile%2F20180609%2F20180609191352_a36e59cff88b5c7578ea595c1c017d21_2.jpeg&h=e2e6c81d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://03.imgmini.eastday.com/mobile/20170401/20170401104813_5509e979d8b3a9342376f4da8b108ec3_8.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F03.imgmini.eastday.com%2Fmobile%2F20170401%2F20170401104813_5509e979d8b3a9342376f4da8b108ec3_8.jpeg&h=82a162ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n柏安妮最經典的一部電影是1990年與張學友和周星馳主演的《咖哩辣椒》，當時她憑著美貌成為不少觀眾心目中的女神。"},{"pid":"56468c3d97c4b544a61a7872cb99081c2571850d","tid":988681,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T09:33:07.000Z","msg":"在1993年拍完《記得香蕉成熟時》便退出了娛樂圈，入讀港大生物學系，並與男同學結婚，生了兩個女兒。婚後，柏安妮再攻讀理大職業治療學系，現在是一名職業治療師。"},{"pid":"3d2208ed8d59008fd83ba031d32df0acb77a485a","tid":988681,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T09:33:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/HVzEKT_seog\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FHVzEKT_seog&d=HiUNBysZrE9nbvaLZxqmO%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=9675ccb1\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/HVzEKT_seog</a><br />\n<br />\n騙我也要一世&nbsp;(1989)<br />\n<br />\n一向對Bossanova有感覺，由林憶蓮《點唱機》到夢劇院《四份三日》，87-89那幾年，出現了幾首輕快作品。《騙我也要一世》愛得咁作賤，要多得周禮茂枝筆。柏安妮是亞視歌手，宣傳比同年新人少 (如草蜢、周慧敏、許志安)，這首歌是《皇家儷人》主題曲。"},{"pid":"7ac7a4f9cc1fc77e960ffaefd0d469fea8ed338f","tid":988681,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T09:37:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Wd-uPGvP38o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FWd-uPGvP38o&d=HiUNBysZrE9nbvaLZxqmO%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=7c729464\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Wd-uPGvP38o</a><br />\n<br />\n不想再擁有 (1988)<br />\n<br />\n來自第一張唱片，電子跳舞節奏，露雲娜也唱過，別怪我一再把她們相提並論，如果你聽過《愛的火花Dynamite》，就知我說什麼。"},{"pid":"81e5447a540d45c6b28024c2fa40ab0b9cb463ce","tid":988681,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T09:48:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://youtu.be/Wd-uPGvP38o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FWd-uPGvP38o&d=HiUNBysZrE9nbvaLZxqmO%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=7c729464\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Wd-uPGvP38o</a><br />\n<br />\n不想再擁有 (1988)<br />\n<br />\n來自第一張唱片，電子跳舞節奏，露雲娜也唱過，別怪我一再把她們相提並論，如果你聽過《愛的火花Dynamite》，就知我說什麼。</blockquote><br />\nlonely nite！disco nite！day n nite！<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/24/014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F24%2F014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png&h=feefedce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"59540827a80fee09f718dc0c740b4e72e118b5d3","tid":988681,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T09:54:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=t4hxtSRwINM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dt4hxtSRwINM&d=HiUNBysZrE9nbvaLZxqmO%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=db244683\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=t4hxtSRwINM</a><br />\n<br />\n沒法拒絕去想你 (1988)"},{"pid":"cdb2ac5176db880b7f03876fbb054401884f30cf","tid":988681,"uid":50663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T10:01:01.000Z","msg":"世界波<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e535a434c40ad03436fa2b5c869e02d75060dde2","tid":988681,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T10:07:54.000Z","msg":"靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbf7ad5a228c6f8c0fba146f46a06f4206e5e37d","tid":988681,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T10:11:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fb8f242901541515a654308ba69fa46ef6566ffa","tid":988681,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T12:26:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/k1MabHGo2xI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fk1MabHGo2xI&d=HiUNBysZrE9nbvaLZxqmO%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=eb4a05e7\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/k1MabHGo2xI</a><br />\n<br />\n魔鬼的火窩 (1988)<br />\n<br />\n做過張國榮《熱辣辣》MV的女主角，她自己有這首情慾歌，歌詞寫到咁，也不用認真，西歌一首，曲式是80年代大熱的Euro Beat，如《傷心的我》、《連鎖反應》等。"},{"pid":"0f3d66e0321e2bbc3a42af2d64e26e584747272a","tid":988681,"uid":182930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T14:02:17.000Z","msg":"對佢啲印象就喺&quot;你老竇有身己己己，恭喜恭喜&quot;"},{"pid":"6e87ec90143cb18ddf019e31dde4aaa20028499f","tid":988681,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T15:20:07.000Z","msg":"幾大波"},{"pid":"da7d8154999eca3f1eee8c3a96be505c7ffdebc2","tid":988681,"uid":1712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T15:21:28.000Z","msg":"世小姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0683a28d89c031aceec4237e02fc88e2b7ec39a4","tid":988681,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T00:53:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/VzPPX6LJMUw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FVzPPX6LJMUw&d=HiUNBysZrE9nbvaLZxqmO%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=696f0caf\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/VzPPX6LJMUw</a><br />\n<br />\n再見昨天&nbsp;(1989)<br />\n<br />\n可能監製想起6 pair半有位錢錢，也是唱得不好但討好的例子，所以請柏安妮再次改編《冷たい雨》(1979)，原曲來自松任谷由實 (未嫁前姓荒井)，錢錢版本出現於1980年，可是小美的《再見昨天》寫得不及鄭國江寫的《冷雨》，舊詞意境較清新。"},{"pid":"16a8d00d5e265d5ec81ccb877fba17e7791ba780","tid":988681,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T05:44:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/01/21/133642_7218e81b9dda6b9852fafdf81768c606.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F01%2F21%2F133642_7218e81b9dda6b9852fafdf81768c606.jpg&h=3c277734&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pic.pimg.tw/elsa339/1201611672.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Felsa339%2F1201611672.jpg&h=4ee181f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n89年張國榮到台灣出國語碟《兜風心情》，與同公司的柏安妮合唱，一起赴台宣傳，合照中有經理人陳淑芬和新藝寶主理人陳少寶，柏安妮和張國榮只合唱這首國語歌，沒合唱廣東歌。柏安妮經理人合約簽陳淑芬公司恒星，跟張國榮同一公司，而新世界鄭裕彤那時入主亞視及入股恒星，恒星旗下的柏安妮、麥潔文、陳潔靈等都簽亞視，張國榮亦在亞姐表演。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/DXVYw3BAZZs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FDXVYw3BAZZs&d=HiUNBysZrE9nbvaLZxqmO%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=a8c52399\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/DXVYw3BAZZs</a>"},{"pid":"b968b520a93464ac3288dc61bcd9c51f26f0ba51","tid":988681,"uid":146435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T10:53:51.000Z","msg":"佢最正係風塵三俠果時"},{"pid":"0be27a78bf65f5de27def4388e6760ef4a846d17","tid":988681,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b968b520a93464ac3288dc61bcd9c51f26f0ba51","tid":988681,"uid":146435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T10:53:51.000Z","msg":"佢最正係風塵三俠果時"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T11:39:50.000Z","msg":"靚到痴線"},{"pid":"1733527d93e503e2dab42e7f4b0fb914265708e6","tid":988681,"uid":21716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T00:49:18.000Z","msg":"成日搞錯佢同關詠荷"},{"pid":"9cea86b4cd643e2a536887b05a2ce39141721b4c","tid":988681,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T03:07:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/01/22/104429_7e8df89156a41883463062f6908e23d3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F01%2F22%2F104429_7e8df89156a41883463062f6908e23d3.jpg&h=9ae7486c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n和柏安妮傳出緋聞的男星，也都大有來頭，其中一位就是梁朝偉。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/01/22/104555_f92458e7ec686a94fdb966f5f3c172e0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F01%2F22%2F104555_f92458e7ec686a94fdb966f5f3c172e0.jpg&h=9d3b6f23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://07imgmini.eastday.com/mobile/20181102/20181102023315_d2cd676c02e2ecbb28db8d9e77f7d9fd_1.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F07imgmini.eastday.com%2Fmobile%2F20181102%2F20181102023315_d2cd676c02e2ecbb28db8d9e77f7d9fd_1.jpeg&h=5ab19c4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://07imgmini.eastday.com/mobile/20181102/20181102023315_d2cd676c02e2ecbb28db8d9e77f7d9fd_15.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F07imgmini.eastday.com%2Fmobile%2F20181102%2F20181102023315_d2cd676c02e2ecbb28db8d9e77f7d9fd_15.jpeg&h=9785452f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n只是這一段感情並不被大家經常提起，因為柏安妮和另一個人的名字更近一些，就是鄭浩南。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20160415/photo/bkn-20160415030424098-0415_00862_001_12p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20160415%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20160415030424098-0415_00862_001_12p.jpg&h=77b61cfe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n鄭浩南是柏安妮唯一承認過的男朋友。<br />\n<br />\n說來也巧，柏安妮在電影中扮演的角色一般都是細化別人，對別人窮追不捨的那一位。<br />\n<br />\n但在現實生活中，是鄭浩南狂追柏安妮，兩個人還是有幾年美好時光的。<br />\n<br />\n可是在兩個人經歷過一段濃情蜜意之後，令人沒想到的是鄭浩南轉身去追張曼玉了，當然這也是據傳！<br />\n<br />\n柏安妮和兩個人的戀愛也正式畫上了句號，坊間一直有傳柏安妮在分手之時給鄭浩南一句話：貪得你有寶咩？<br />\n<br />\n然後非常冷酷地就走了~真是揮一揮衣袖不帶走一片雲彩！"},{"pid":"b7a402f4ad6950a4ec6279e1e38d5ac143416ba0","tid":988681,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T03:12:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/nHA9eaaNK1Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FnHA9eaaNK1Q&d=HiUNBysZrE9nbvaLZxqmO%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=0589a79d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/nHA9eaaNK1Q</a><br />\n不夜天 (1989)<br />\n<br />\n除了Bossanova，又有這首Jazzy嘢，同年，林憶蓮有《回家對著你媽媽》，鄺美雲就有《Fever》，均是輕撫絲襪意態撩人那種歌，三首歸類為同系產品。"}]}